00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:04.000
whom we believe to be the last of a series of prophets,

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:10.000
beginning with Adam, including Noah, including Moses, including Abraham,

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:14.000
